{
  "text": "\u2022 Disagreement based exploration: In this approach, if any two classifiers in the hypothesis class disagree on whether a person is likely to be infected or not, then that person should be tested. However, this algorithm is somewhat challenging to implement. One version of the algorithm is implemented here [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
